Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:27.75,tittle,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「千尋來了！」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 千尋？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到「た」還以為是竹原站
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急急忙忙下車卻發現是忠海站
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.24,0:02:50.36,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}竹原驛「たけはらえき」和忠海驛「ただのうみえき」第一個假名相同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒~~？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我馬上去坐下一班電車
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離下一班電車還有一個鐘頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋 你等等 我問問媽媽有沒有人能開車來接你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.86,0:03:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠海？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 離下一班電車還有一個鐘頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去接她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓就回玉響等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.47,0:03:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是借來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽騎著摩托車
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.62,0:03:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏也有摩托車
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…小楓？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你長大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾位是曾經關照過你媽媽的摩托車旅行俱樂部的車手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你出生的時候我們大家都來看過你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼小的嬰兒竟然變得那麼漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 是年紀大了的緣故嗎 最近眼睛變得容易出汗了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 要看看珠江以前的照片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我想看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠江以前可是很帥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人雖小卻能將摩托車駕馭自如呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也長大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以來邀請她一起去久違的摩托車旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽和摩托車
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想坐一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了 回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經開得很慢了 你怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓 好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待著這次的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你發郵件哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是媽媽給的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 千尋已經到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章魚的天婦羅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為千尋喜歡章魚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也吃吃看 吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡廣島菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…是因為章魚很好吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.71,0:06:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為小楓過得很開心 笑得那麼自然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 總覺得放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋跟楓從小學開始就在一起了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小楓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好嗎 軟呼呼之助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交了很多朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天給你介紹小薰她們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.74,0:07:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你每天都有拍照嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然拍的不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能讓你看看竹原了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音碳真是的 太緊張了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪的朋友 好像是個愛哭鬼吧 薰碳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯 特別愛掉眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 別叫我薰碳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要注意淚腺開關對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多耀眼的香碳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想萌死我乃理惠碳嗎 是嗎～！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不小心把心裏話說出來了 不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫三次千尋 這次…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋 讓你看到這樣的場面了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫岡崎乃理惠  多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是塙薰 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是櫻田麻音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點去吃大阪燒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽香碳的 去吃吧 去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新菜單 保幌燒 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香味真好聞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.70,0:09:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃點 要戰勝夏天的炎熱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香碳 很燙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你吹吹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎 不燙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就是用這個吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個很燙的 小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋是第一次來竹原吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒~ 那得帶著到處逛逛才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.76,0:09:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪 去哪裏好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏還有那個…然後…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛嘛 別著急
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的被叫做小啪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在這邊大家都叫我小啪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯 我老姐是看了小啪走路的樣子後取的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓×N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是剛上小學的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰要玩躲避球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.89,0:10:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三次千尋？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,0:10:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤渡…小楓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋和我都不太會交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不正有個適合的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱抱地藏？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊許願邊抱起地藏大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說如果比想像的要輕得多的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼願望就能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 也是呢 是石頭來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情緒低落時果然要吃二重燒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在高處吃的話 情緒就會更…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高漲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.69,0:12:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 這風景
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 煙囪那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到海哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時會跟大家一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好的地方吧 千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情緒沒有高漲 甜點和美景也不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.44,0:12:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 剛才我情緒高漲起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.97,0:12:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:13:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛 太可愛了 這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情緒十分高漲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圓圓的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾啊滾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是桃貓大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃貓大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺不錯啊 情緒高漲起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一口氣升到最高點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姐來短信了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐要來了真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是絕好的探險日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔鬼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 無視無視
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒~？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無視我真過分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.84,0:13:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾時來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:14:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 大家去黑瀧山那裏 提高情緒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑瀧山？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 要用車
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖的駕駛又再次…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走路？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 提起精神走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走到黑瀧山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.05,0:14:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 這樣好的探險日怎能用車呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比佐代美駕駛要好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能這麼想了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠海是我下錯的車站嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會很遠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:42.58,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一小時後。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:50.99,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩小時後…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐電車不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.41,0:15:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 休息五分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:26.20,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三小時後…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.58,0:15:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點就要到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃苦味檸檬汽水糖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦味檸檬汽水糖？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 乃理惠我手工做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要那麼可疑的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以拒絕的 千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:15:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不吃我的苦味檸檬汽水糖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不及格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給香碳吃什麼的 是我乃理惠一生最珍藏的幸福 來 請品嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃多點 吃多少都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是千尋手工做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋喜歡可愛的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口笛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 還差一點就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是一直都「還差一點」麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.47,0:17:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了登山道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要開始爬黑瀧山了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.17,0:17:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.69,0:17:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好做準備體操哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.35,0:17:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備體操兩分鐘？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 因為到山頂要二三十分鐘的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:17:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡搞？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手工做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新角色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個好地方呢 小楓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是第一次來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和千尋一起到一個第一次去的地方 真高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓有好好生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好好地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你為我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來淚腺的開關是那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現小香了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交朋友真困難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很不擅長交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人向你搭話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上 軟乎乎之助的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這孩子叫軟乎乎之助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有說它可愛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.14,0:19:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 有讓我看自己做的吉祥物的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.81,0:20:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛 做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.11,0:20:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們也是千尋的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.66,0:20:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我試試向那孩子搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家能收下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅蒙蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝶浮羅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若比利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊萬鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土沙沙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 蝶浮羅 過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.74,0:20:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交換郵箱地址吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 淚腺的開關又…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰 乃理惠 麻音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 軟乎乎之助 要再來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.67,0:21:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次要登上黑瀧山的山頂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.91,0:21:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我姐的恐怖留言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.84,0:21:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.71,0:21:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你能來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.37,0:22:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到小楓交到了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.76,0:22:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實有點寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.03,0:22:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在已經
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.29,0:22:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使分隔兩地 不管過了多少年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一直是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.76,0:22:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.06,0:22:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個地方相遇的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不會消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.61,0:22:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後面對與今後相遇的人的新回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.90,0:22:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要變得積極
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.31,0:24:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.03,0:24:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那是哪一天的事」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.90,0:24:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「然後某天的事」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.84,0:23:09.27,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}君が指でつくるフレームには
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.36,0:23:15.81,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}蒲公英の綿毛が映りこむよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.95,0:23:22.08,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}格子窗 竹細工 急な階段
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.18,0:23:28.43,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}懷かしい景色もそのままだね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.11,0:23:35.06,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}そこにある何氣ないこと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.92,0:23:41.23,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}手のひらからこぼれてても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.21,0:23:48.29,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}恐れないで 止まらないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.81,0:23:54.69,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}君は君のままでいて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.85,0:24:01.62,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}神樣は時々惡戲する
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.93,0:24:14.47,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}一番大切なものだけを どこかに置き去りにさせて
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.63,0:24:21.24,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}僕たちを大人にするんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.65,0:24:28.55,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}君を大人にするんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.84,0:23:09.27,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}在你手做的框架上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.36,0:23:15.81,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}映照著蒲公英的絨毛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.95,0:23:22.08,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}格子窗 竹工藝品 陡峭的樓梯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.18,0:23:28.43,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}令人懷念的景色還是如舊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.11,0:23:35.06,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}存在在那的無意之事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.92,0:23:41.23,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}即使從手心中溢出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.21,0:23:48.29,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}也請不要害怕 請不要止步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.81,0:23:54.69,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}請你如常
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.85,0:24:01.62,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}神有時會惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.93,0:24:14.47,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}讓人把最重要的事物棄之不顧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.63,0:24:21.24,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}把我們變成大人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.65,0:24:28.55,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}把你變成大人
